* Notice
The code is well merged into a new plantuml-mode by Skuro (https://github.com/skuro/plantuml-mode).
It is now available on MELPA.

* Introduction

This is a major mode for plantuml(http://plantuml.sourceforge.net/)

Plantuml is an open-source tool in java that allows to quickly write :
    - sequence diagram,
    - use case diagram,
    - class diagram,
    - activity diagram,
    - component diagram,
    - state diagram
    - object diagram

using a simple and intuitive language.
